CVT(TR690)-83
Transmission Mounting System
CONTINUOUSLY VARIABLE TRANSMISSION
11.Transmission Mounting System
A: REMOVAL
1. PITCHING STOPPER
1) Disconnect the ground terminal from battery sensor. <Ref. to NT-5, BATTERY, NOTE, Note.>
2) Remove the intercooler. <Ref. to IN(w/o STI)-38, REMOVAL, Intercooler.>
3) Remove the pitching stopper.
2. TRANSMISSION REAR CROSSMEMBER AND REAR CUSHION RUBBER
1) Disconnect the ground terminal from battery sensor. <Ref. to NT-5, BATTERY, NOTE, Note.>
2) Lift up the vehicle.
3) Remove the center exhaust pipe (rear). <Ref. to EX(w/o STI)-35, REMOVAL, Center Exhaust Pipe.>
4) Remove the center exhaust cover.

5) Set the transmission jack under the transmission. Make sure that the support plate of transmission jack
does not touch the oil pan.
6) Remove the transmission rear crossmember.
7) Remove the rear cushion rubber.

CVT(TR690)-85
Transmission Mounting System
CONTINUOUSLY VARIABLE TRANSMISSION
B: INSTALLATION
1. PITCHING STOPPER
1) Install the pitching stopper.
Tightening torque:
T1: 50 Nm (5.1 kgf-m, 36.9 ft-lb)
T2: 58 Nm (5.9 kgf-m, 42.8 ft-lb)
2) Install the intercooler. <Ref. to IN(w/o STI)-41, INSTALLATION, Intercooler.>
3) Connect the ground terminal to battery sensor. <Ref. to NT-5, BATTERY, NOTE, Note.>
2. TRANSMISSION REAR CROSSMEMBER AND REAR CUSHION RUBBER
1) Install the rear cushion rubber.
Tightening torque:
40 Nm (4.1 kgf-m, 29.5 ft-lb)
CVT00491

T2
AT-07338

CVT(TR690)-86
Transmission Mounting System
CONTINUOUSLY VARIABLE TRANSMISSION
2) Install the transmission rear crossmember.
Tightening torque:
T1: 35 Nm (3.6 kgf-m, 25.8 ft-lb)
T2: 70 Nm (7.1 kgf-m, 51.6 ft-lb)
3) Remove the transmission jack.
4) Install the center exhaust cover.
Tightening torque:
18 Nm (1.8 kgf-m, 13.3 ft-lb)
5) Install the center exhaust pipe (rear). <Ref. to EX(w/o STI)-41, INSTALLATION, Center Exhaust Pipe.>
6) Connect the ground terminal to battery sensor. <Ref. to NT-5, BATTERY, NOTE, Note.>
C: INSPECTION
Check the crossmember for bends or damage.
Check that the cushion rubber is not stiff, cracked or otherwise damaged.
